- Just take the picture.

40:15.455 --> 40:17.164
Well, that's a keeper.

40:17.499 --> 40:19.124
Let me see it.

40:20.460 --> 40:21.919
Why she wants dozens of reminders

40:22.003 --> 40:24.630
