57:05.506 --> 57:06.923
<i>Flash back</i>

57:07.007 --> 57:09.175
<i>To warm nights</i>

57:09.426 --> 57:11.844
<i>Almost left behind</i>

57:12.763 --> 57:16.766
<i>Suitcase of memories</i>

57:16.850 --> 57:18.434
<i>Time after</i>

57:18.519 --> 57:21.354
<i>Sometimes you picture me...</i> 

