57:33.033 --> 57:34.700
You're so cool.

57:35.202 --> 57:37.203
Mr. Empty Backpack.

57:38.705 --> 57:40.498
- You know about my backpack?
- I googled you.

57:40.582 --> 57:41.833
You did?

57:41.917 --> 57:44.460
