What happened to Alex?

01:00:44.933 --> 01:00:47.018
She had to leave town early
to get to a meeting.

01:00:47.102 --> 01:00:50.271
- That's too bad. Where does she live?
- Chicago.

01:00:51.523 --> 01:00:53.065
Thinking of going to see her?

01:00:53.150 --> 01:00:55.484
We don't really have that kind of relationship. 
Try right over there.

01:00:55.569 --> 01:00:57.153
That direction.

01:00:57.654 --> 01:01:00.906
What kind of relationship do you have?

01:01:01.450 --> 01:01:03.534
Well, you know, casual.

01:01:04.661 --> 01:01:07.413
- Sounds pretty special.
- It works for us.

01:01:09.708 --> 01:01:12.126
Don't you think there's a future there?

